	<clause id="_decoupling_cryptographic_primitives_in_trust_stores" obligation="normative"><title>Decoupling cryptographic primitives in trust stores</title><clause id="_challenges" obligation="normative"><title>Challenges</title><p id="_fcfb4a1c-fc38-4f3f-b4cb-d8bd904d2a61">Traditional cross-platform trust stores are challenged in many ways, including:</p>
