	<clause id="_the_confium_trust_store" obligation="normative"><title>The Confium trust store</title><clause id="_purpose" obligation="normative">
	<title>Purpose</title>
	<p id="_0e6bd3ad-618d-432a-8b5c-ec5867f9e196">Confium is an extensible secure keystore framework for threshold cryptography and beyond. It aims to be an interoperable trust store, that is platform independent and relies on international standards to ensure its contents are portable.</p>
	</clause>
	<clause id="_background_2" obligation="normative"><title>Background</title><p id="_cc483d18-6bb4-40df-86d5-ddadd7c46cbc">Confium is an offshoot of RNP, an open-source, open-licensed (BSD) OpenPGP library and toolkit. Both Confium and RNP are developed by Ribose.</p>
