	<clause id="_structure" obligation="normative"><title>Structure</title><clause id="_overview_2" obligation="normative"><title>Overview</title><p id="_76821fce-e646-4bae-9d3f-70ab9d950dcf">Confium provides a new keystore framework consisting of 3 layers:</p>
	<ol id="_329495f4-1bc4-40f3-8508-8ea0938c062a" type="arabic">
