	<clause id="_information_about_ribose" obligation="normative"><title>Information about Ribose</title><clause id="_general_6" obligation="normative"><title>General</title><p id="_7deb8a3d-8c61-482b-8f8d-be2445ba655b">Ribose Group Inc. (BVI, with its wholly owned subsidiary, Ribose Inc., based in Delaware) is a pioneer of interoperable and cybersecurity technologies across user-centric systems and applications. It has been named a Deloitte Technology FAST 20 Rising Star and Red Herring Global 100 company, and has received CSA’s Enterprise Award for Security Innovation of the Year.</p>
	<p id="_7f64449a-5444-4d5d-98b3-5871315c7fb3">Ribose is the world’s first organization to be certified to the NIST Cybersecurity Framework by BSI, with its experience presented at the inaugural NIST Risk Management Conference in 2018.</p>
	<p id="_ee6258d3-2416-4e89-807b-7130d2e95785">Ribose is certified by BSI to <eref type="inline" bibitemid="ISO-IEC_27001" citeas="ISO/IEC 27001 (all parts)"/>, <eref type="inline" bibitemid="ISO-IEC_27017" citeas="ISO/IEC 27017:2015"/>, <eref type="inline" bibitemid="ISO-IEC_27018" citeas="ISO/IEC 27018 (all parts)"/> and <eref type="inline" bibitemid="ISO-IEC_27701" citeas="ISO/IEC 27701:2019"/>, <eref type="inline" bibitemid="ISO-IEC_22301" citeas="ISO/IEC 22301"/>, <eref type="inline" bibitemid="ISO-IEC_20000-1" citeas="ISO/IEC 20000-1"/>, <eref type="inline" bibitemid="ISO_9001" citeas="ISO 9001 (all parts)"/>, CSA STAR Certification, amongst other schemes.</p></clause>
	<clause id="_experience_with_nist" obligation="normative"><title>Experience with NIST</title><p id="_356a72b1-7a6c-4528-994f-9a1eca94e486">Ribose is the world’s first organization to be certified to the NIST Cybersecurity Framework by BSI, with its experience presented at the inaugural NIST Risk Management Conference in 2018.</p>
	<p id="_9fd27462-bec3-4460-a866-25b7ca9983b8">Ribose’s Metanorma framework is currently being piloted by NIST’s Computer Security Division for the publication of the Special Publications 800 series and Cybersecurity Whitepaper documents.</p>


